    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to the world of Dracamar!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Embark on a beautiful 3D platformer adventure and fight King Crad, the evil dragon who wants to conquer the world of Dracamar. Run, jump, and fight the evil forces to rescue the magical Okis!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world of Dracamar is inspired by the Mediterranean landscapes and culture, reflecting positive human values in a cozy experience. The game portrays a balanced lifestyle in harmony with nature based on friendship, generosity, and togetherness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306480/extras/c4687333b25e0df9b421768572f5b8f3.poster.avif?t=1772471432\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306480/extras/c4687333b25e0df9b421768572f5b8f3.webm?t=1772471432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306480/extras/c4687333b25e0df9b421768572f5b8f3.mp4?t=1772471432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Friends that travel together, stay together!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Travel and explore all the islands and free the Okis. Collect Moki-balls and use their energy to rebuild the bridges and connect the islands again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the shores of the Mediterranean Sea to the Pyrenees Mountains, this epic adventure shows how great life can be when we all have the support of our community.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306480/extras/eecf1992618bebb42f68f60a2194994f.poster.avif?t=1772471432\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306480/extras/eecf1992618bebb42f68f60a2194994f.webm?t=1772471432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306480/extras/eecf1992618bebb42f68f60a2194994f.mp4?t=1772471432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Heroes come in all shapes and sizes!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet Iko, who is a very special Oki. He will follow you on your adventures and help you defeat King Crad with his magical powers. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306480/extras/ce0ba9d6c543d547e922b4a38fe6d523.poster.avif?t=1772471432\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306480/extras/ce0ba9d6c543d547e922b4a38fe6d523.webm?t=1772471432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306480/extras/ce0ba9d6c543d547e922b4a38fe6d523.mp4?t=1772471432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a colorful world of islands with eye-candy visuals!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 playable characters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15 levels full of enemies, traps, challenges, and puzzles, plus 5 secret bonus levels. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautifully-rendered graphics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover all kinds of hidden gems, challenges, and collectibles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Designed to delight and challenge players of all ages and skill levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn more about the Catalan culture, which has a strong influence on the world of Dracamar (the game is also localized into Catalan).</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A production by<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306480/extras/992b309e312f5134c45a0abfcbff40ad.webp?t=1772471432\" width=200 height=58 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >in collaboration with<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306480/extras/6d88c53a8d2ab645ba7656f54a6b7fe3.avif?t=1772471432\" width=150 height=104 /></span></p>",
